1
00:00:17,600 --> 00:00:19,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank goodness, bro...</font>

2
00:00:20,030 --> 00:00:23,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro! 
Master Seiichiro, hold on!</font>

3
00:00:23,400 --> 00:00:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But how? It didn't hit him!</font>

4
00:00:26,160 --> 00:00:28,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Ist, what's going on?</font>

5
00:00:29,750 --> 00:00:33,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I knew it. His barrier is gone.</font>

6
00:00:36,310 --> 00:00:37,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Smooch.</font>

7
00:00:39,820 --> 00:00:41,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No good, huh?</font>

8
00:00:41,510 --> 00:00:43,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">M-Master Ist!</font>

9
00:00:43,120 --> 00:00:45,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you doing during an 
emergency in our holy church?!</font>

10
00:00:46,140 --> 00:00:48,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">As I suspected, it's best
 if it's the same person.</font>

11
00:00:48,970 --> 00:00:51,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Priest, you have a lot of magical energy.</font>

12
00:00:51,540 --> 00:00:53,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you saying?</font>

13
00:00:53,530 --> 00:00:55,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We need to take him to the infirmary!</font>

14
00:00:55,180 --> 00:00:56,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, you can't.</font>

15
00:00:56,900 --> 00:01:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you take Kondu to 
the infirmary, he'll die.</font>

16
00:01:00,820 --> 00:01:04,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So won't you sleep with him?</font>

17
00:01:05,680 --> 00:01:06,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

18
00:01:06,710 --> 00:01:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, didn't you just cast 
a barrier on Kondu?</font>

19
00:01:10,900 --> 00:01:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did.</font>

20
00:01:12,010 --> 00:01:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, you didn't know that Kondu
 has no resistance to magical energy?</font>

21
00:01:18,820 --> 00:01:22,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right now, Kondu is experiencing 
acute magic-sickness.</font>

22
00:01:22,340 --> 00:01:24,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You need to acclimate him 
to the magical energy</font>

23
00:01:24,400 --> 00:01:26,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">or it's going to go berserk inside of him.</font>

24
00:01:27,000 --> 00:01:28,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then that's why you...</font>

25
00:01:28,960 --> 00:01:29,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

26
00:01:29,940 --> 00:01:33,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it looks like mouth-to-mouth 
wasn't anywhere close to enough.</font>

27
00:01:33,280 --> 00:01:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, it's better if 
the caster does the acclimating,</font>

28
00:01:36,490 --> 00:01:39,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so please infuse your 
magical energy inside him.</font>

29
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That's...</font>

30
00:01:43,530 --> 00:01:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

31
00:01:47,620 --> 00:01:49,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No need!</font>

32
00:02:02,800 --> 00:02:07,940
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}ISEKAI OFFICE WORKER: THE OTHER WORLD'S 
BOOKS DEPEND ON THE BEAN COUNTER</font>

33
00:03:20,010 --> 00:03:24,970
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 11: I GOT HOSPITALIZED</font>

34
00:03:25,090 --> 00:03:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh!</font>

35
00:03:28,720 --> 00:03:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the one who manages 
everything for him.</font>

36
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give him back to me.</font>

37
00:03:32,600 --> 00:03:34,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Give him back"?</font>

38
00:03:34,300 --> 00:03:36,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro isn't an object.</font>

39
00:03:36,770 --> 00:03:39,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Moreover, he's very weak right now.</font>

40
00:03:40,010 --> 00:03:41,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I won't hand him to you.</font>

41
00:03:43,850 --> 00:03:46,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama?</font>

42
00:03:47,760 --> 00:03:50,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro! You're awake!</font>

43
00:03:50,960 --> 00:03:52,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou!</font>

44
00:03:53,790 --> 00:03:56,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, thank goodness.</font>

45
00:03:56,890 --> 00:03:58,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're safe...</font>

46
00:04:00,780 --> 00:04:01,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siegvold.</font>

47
00:04:02,510 --> 00:04:03,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your Highness...</font>

48
00:04:04,520 --> 00:04:07,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh normally sees to Kondou's health.</font>

49
00:04:07,930 --> 00:04:10,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You can leave everything to him.</font>

50
00:04:10,010 --> 00:04:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relinquish the man.</font>

51
00:04:13,370 --> 00:04:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I understand.</font>

52
00:04:18,110 --> 00:04:21,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Will Master Seiichiro be all right?</font>

53
00:04:21,380 --> 00:04:23,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, probably.</font>

54
00:04:23,580 --> 00:04:26,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-san is used to taking care of him.</font>

55
00:04:26,160 --> 00:04:26,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

56
00:04:29,780 --> 00:04:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quellbus!</font>

57
00:04:31,310 --> 00:04:33,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm going to use the back room.</font>

58
00:04:33,060 --> 00:04:35,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're not some cheap inn for quick flings.</font>

59
00:04:38,510 --> 00:04:40,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's definitely magic-sick,</font>

60
00:04:40,570 --> 00:04:42,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but there's always a chance
 it's something else.</font>

61
00:04:43,310 --> 00:04:47,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's better to have someone on hand
who can explain or respond appropriately.</font>

62
00:04:47,320 --> 00:04:49,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Explain, huh?</font>

63
00:04:51,830 --> 00:04:53,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh...</font>

64
00:04:53,540 --> 00:04:56,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many magical energy recovery 
tonics have you had today?</font>

65
00:04:57,110 --> 00:04:58,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One.</font>

66
00:04:58,420 --> 00:05:00,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't lie.</font>

67
00:05:00,110 --> 00:05:03,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You probably drank one to acclimate 
Kondu on your way here, too.</font>

68
00:05:03,720 --> 00:05:05,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In your current state 
of relying on medication,</font>

69
00:05:05,890 --> 00:05:10,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">using enough magical energy to treat 
him will take too much out of you.</font>

70
00:05:10,350 --> 00:05:11,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know.</font>

71
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:13,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I came here.</font>

72
00:05:15,020 --> 00:05:16,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about me.</font>

73
00:05:16,860 --> 00:05:20,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know my magical energy limits best.</font>

74
00:05:26,220 --> 00:05:29,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't do anything too reckless.</font>

75
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:35,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's so hot...</i></font>

76
00:05:35,750 --> 00:05:39,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My head and my whole body hurt.</i></font>

77
00:05:40,120 --> 00:05:44,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It reminds me of that time I had the flu.</i></font>

78
00:05:44,150 --> 00:05:49,160
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}MEDICINE</font>

79
00:05:45,070 --> 00:05:48,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I didn't get any rest until 
I collapsed from the fever.</i></font>

80
00:05:48,090 --> 00:05:51,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was still getting work files 
while I couldn't go into the office,</i></font>

81
00:05:51,100 --> 00:05:53,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and my fever spiked to 40 degrees Celsius.</i></font>

82
00:05:54,230 --> 00:05:58,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like my consciousness is 
more faded than it was back then,</i></font>

83
00:05:58,490 --> 00:06:00,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but I'm not uncomfortable.</i></font>

84
00:06:00,430 --> 00:06:02,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In fact, I'm nice and warm...</i></font>

85
00:06:02,820 --> 00:06:06,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's soothing, 
like soaking in a hot spring.</i></font>

86
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:09,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I remember this feeling...</i></font>

87
00:06:13,600 --> 00:06:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama?</font>

88
00:06:15,310 --> 00:06:17,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You finally woke up...</font>

89
00:06:17,820 --> 00:06:18,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good grief.</font>

90
00:06:19,240 --> 00:06:21,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's still going to take some time.</font>

91
00:06:21,530 --> 00:06:24,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're such a reckless fool.</font>

92
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When did you get back?</font>

93
00:06:26,550 --> 00:06:27,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This morning.</font>

94
00:06:28,060 --> 00:06:31,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The instant I returned,
 I found out you went to the church,</font>

95
00:06:31,380 --> 00:06:33,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so I immediately headed there.</font>

96
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:35,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I barely made it in time.</font>

97
00:06:36,190 --> 00:06:38,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I swear, you're so...</font>

98
00:06:39,020 --> 00:06:43,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You never listen to anyone, and you 
have no regard for your own well-being.</font>

99
00:06:43,740 --> 00:06:46,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is what happens the second 
I take my eyes off of you.</font>

100
00:06:46,250 --> 00:06:49,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On top of that, you didn't 
send me a single letter</font>

101
00:06:49,590 --> 00:06:53,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and wound up collapsing
 into another man's arms!</font>

102
00:06:54,480 --> 00:06:59,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Honestly, if it weren't for <i>that</i>, 
I might not forgive you.</font>

103
00:07:00,470 --> 00:07:01,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama...</font>

104
00:07:03,440 --> 00:07:04,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back.</font>

105
00:07:11,450 --> 00:07:12,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

106
00:07:17,050 --> 00:07:19,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, he seems to be fine now.</font>

107
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:21,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm heading back to the estate.</font>

108
00:07:21,690 --> 00:07:24,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep an eye on Seiichirou 
once he wakes up.</font>

109
00:07:24,910 --> 00:07:26,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep an eye on him?</font>

110
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:27,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, Aresh!</font>

111
00:07:28,140 --> 00:07:31,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After that, I was ordered to stay 
hospitalized for three days.</i></font>

112
00:07:33,050 --> 00:07:34,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's now the second day.</i></font>

113
00:07:34,870 --> 00:07:37,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I haven't seen Aresh-sama since.</i></font>

114
00:07:38,000 --> 00:07:42,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seriously, I was so shocked 
when I heard you collapsed!</font>

115
00:07:42,590 --> 00:07:45,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that. 
Where are the documents?</font>

116
00:07:45,090 --> 00:07:45,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

117
00:07:45,880 --> 00:07:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came to visit you, but now it looks 
like I only came to make you work...</font>

118
00:07:51,350 --> 00:07:54,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Speaking of visitors,
 immediately after I awoke...</i></font>

119
00:07:55,270 --> 00:07:58,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, I offer you
my sincerest apologies!</font>

120
00:07:58,660 --> 00:08:02,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, no... There's no need 
for you to apologize.</font>

121
00:08:02,540 --> 00:08:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please raise your head.</font>

122
00:08:04,990 --> 00:08:10,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. I knew you had no 
resistance to magical energy,</font>

123
00:08:10,490 --> 00:08:13,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">yet I still exposed you to such danger.</font>

124
00:08:13,860 --> 00:08:18,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault that I wasn't doing well 
that day due to lack of sleep,</font>

125
00:08:18,140 --> 00:08:21,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and going to the chapel 
was entirely my decision.</font>

126
00:08:22,120 --> 00:08:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, I probably 
would have died instantly</font>

127
00:08:25,100 --> 00:08:26,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">if you hadn't cast that barrier on me.</font>

128
00:08:28,840 --> 00:08:32,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much for saving me.</font>

129
00:08:34,890 --> 00:08:37,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, about that...</font>

130
00:08:41,090 --> 00:08:43,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu, you have a visitor.</font>

131
00:08:43,130 --> 00:08:44,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll take my leave.</font>

132
00:08:44,810 --> 00:08:46,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please don't overexert yourself.</font>

133
00:08:52,750 --> 00:08:54,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Valtom-san...</font>

134
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:57,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How are you doing, Kondu-sama?</font>

135
00:08:57,510 --> 00:09:00,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks to Aresh-sama, 
I've already made a full recovery,</font>

136
00:09:00,850 --> 00:09:04,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I was told to take every 
precaution and rest until tomorrow.</font>

137
00:09:05,610 --> 00:09:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's excellent news.</font>

138
00:09:08,520 --> 00:09:12,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama has informed me that he will 
fetch you when it is time to return home.</font>

139
00:09:13,580 --> 00:09:14,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see...</font>

140
00:09:17,200 --> 00:09:20,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The young master is currently 
recuperating at the estate.</font>

141
00:09:20,930 --> 00:09:21,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

142
00:09:21,720 --> 00:09:28,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">To be precise, he has fallen ill from an
 excessive amount of recovery tonics.</font>

143
00:09:28,950 --> 00:09:32,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The purification expedition,
 the magic beast subjugation,</font>

144
00:09:32,510 --> 00:09:35,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and then immediately acclimating 
magical energy upon his return</font>

145
00:09:35,840 --> 00:09:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">placed considerable strain 
on even the young master,</font>

146
00:09:38,520 --> 00:09:40,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">whose magic reserves are vast.</font>

147
00:09:41,750 --> 00:09:43,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that's what happened...</i></font>

148
00:09:43,800 --> 00:09:45,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I thought it was strange.</i></font>

149
00:09:45,790 --> 00:09:49,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He treated me at the infirmary 
instead of at home.</i></font>

150
00:09:50,070 --> 00:09:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Usually, Aresh-sama would have taken
 me there to keep an eye on me himself.</i></font>

151
00:09:56,990 --> 00:09:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu-sama.</font>

152
00:09:59,670 --> 00:10:01,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I have known the young master,</font>

153
00:10:01,890 --> 00:10:04,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama, since he was a child, 
and have had the privilege</font>

154
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">of attending to his needs all these years.</font>

155
00:10:06,880 --> 00:10:10,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It may be presumptuous of a mere 
steward like myself to say as much,</font>

156
00:10:10,590 --> 00:10:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I harbor feelings for him 
akin to those of a parent.</font>

157
00:10:16,200 --> 00:10:18,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, Kondu-sama...</font>

158
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:23,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know that what I am about to ask runs
contrary to the young master's wishes.</font>

159
00:10:23,870 --> 00:10:29,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My top priority is safeguarding 
the young master's health.</font>

160
00:10:30,150 --> 00:10:31,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right.</font>

161
00:10:31,520 --> 00:10:35,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since meeting you, 
the young master has changed.</font>

162
00:10:36,850 --> 00:10:38,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He has shed his former lethargy</font>

163
00:10:38,960 --> 00:10:41,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and became more vibrant than
 I have ever seen him before.</font>

164
00:10:42,120 --> 00:10:49,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It brings me joy that the young 
master has fallen in love,</font>

165
00:10:49,060 --> 00:10:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and in my eyes, you are the savior 
who has given him the vitality to live.</font>

166
00:10:55,770 --> 00:10:56,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However...</font>

167
00:10:56,920 --> 00:11:00,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That is all contingent on 
the young master's health.</font>

168
00:11:02,050 --> 00:11:05,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Though I believe the young master's 
feelings are important,</font>

169
00:11:05,540 --> 00:11:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I desire that he see to his 
well-being above all else.</font>

170
00:11:09,550 --> 00:11:13,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Perhaps that is merely the 
sentiment of an old man.</font>

171
00:11:14,290 --> 00:11:16,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, you're absolutely right.</font>

172
00:11:17,580 --> 00:11:21,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been too dependent on Aresh-sama.</font>

173
00:11:22,480 --> 00:11:26,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I have a habit of prioritizing work 
while neglecting my own health.</i></font>

174
00:11:26,960 --> 00:11:30,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now I've compromised 
Aresh-sama's health, as well.</i></font>

175
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:33,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The monster subjugation 
is a perfect example.</i></font>

176
00:11:33,590 --> 00:11:38,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The very one putting Aresh in peril is me.</i></font>

177
00:11:40,330 --> 00:11:43,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry. This is all 
a failure on my part.</font>

178
00:11:43,700 --> 00:11:46,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">There is no need to apologize to me.</font>

179
00:11:46,900 --> 00:11:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After all, I'm sure the young 
master decided on his own</font>

180
00:11:50,330 --> 00:11:53,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to subjugate the magic beasts 
purely to impress you.</font>

181
00:11:54,540 --> 00:11:58,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, even if it means 
incurring his resentment,</font>

182
00:11:58,690 --> 00:12:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wish to protect the 
young master's health.</font>

183
00:12:03,530 --> 00:12:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please remember one thing.</font>

184
00:12:07,100 --> 00:12:12,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Many of us would be at a loss
if you were to fall ill.</font>

185
00:12:15,570 --> 00:12:17,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well? How are you feeling?</font>

186
00:12:18,100 --> 00:12:22,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm doing great, thanks to you. 
I was able to get some proper rest.</font>

187
00:12:22,000 --> 00:12:25,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didn't you have your subordinates 
bring you documents to work on?</font>

188
00:12:25,710 --> 00:12:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I haven't done much of it.</font>

189
00:12:27,680 --> 00:12:29,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, regarding my bill...</font>

190
00:12:29,350 --> 00:12:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, don't worry about that. 
You're a civil servant, Kondu.</font>

191
00:12:33,710 --> 00:12:36,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So this is one of the perks of 
working at the royal palace!</i></font>

192
00:12:37,990 --> 00:12:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look a lot better.</font>

193
00:12:42,680 --> 00:12:44,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You got here pretty early.</font>

194
00:12:50,400 --> 00:12:52,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He looks like his regular self.</i></font>

195
00:12:53,140 --> 00:12:58,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If Valtom-san hadn't told me, I might 
have never known that he was bedridden.</i></font>

196
00:12:59,520 --> 00:13:01,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry for worrying you.</font>

197
00:13:01,560 --> 00:13:02,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Indeed.</font>

198
00:13:03,480 --> 00:13:05,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm guessing one of the reasons</i></font>

199
00:13:05,800 --> 00:13:09,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>he wanted me hospitalized here was 
so I wouldn't see him in that state.</i></font>

200
00:13:11,100 --> 00:13:13,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You feel hot. Do you still have a fever?</font>

201
00:13:13,940 --> 00:13:15,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}No, I'm fine.</font>

202
00:13:15,250 --> 00:13:18,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, why don't you save all that 
affection for when you get home?</font>

203
00:13:15,870 --> 00:13:16,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Really?</font>

204
00:13:16,930 --> 00:13:17,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Really.</font>

205
00:13:17,730 --> 00:13:19,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}You're not pushing 
yourself again, are you?</font>

206
00:13:18,660 --> 00:13:21,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How many times must I tell you
the infirmary isn't the place for that?</font>

207
00:13:21,840 --> 00:13:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, Kondu, you're going home already?</font>

208
00:13:25,200 --> 00:13:28,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san and... Sigma-kun?</font>

209
00:13:28,580 --> 00:13:31,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">G-Good morning.</font>

210
00:13:34,750 --> 00:13:35,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that?</font>

211
00:13:35,750 --> 00:13:37,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The child who made my abacus.</font>

212
00:13:38,520 --> 00:13:40,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why are the two of you together?</font>

213
00:13:40,470 --> 00:13:44,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san invited me to see 
the sorcery department.</font>

214
00:13:44,500 --> 00:13:47,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We got to talking about a magic
 tool when we met at the church,</font>

215
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:50,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and he asked me to make 
one together with him.</font>

216
00:13:50,330 --> 00:13:51,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?!</font>

217
00:13:51,610 --> 00:13:56,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I love woodworking, but I've 
always admired magic tools...</font>

218
00:13:57,040 --> 00:13:59,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But crafting them costs a fortune.</font>

219
00:13:59,690 --> 00:14:01,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought the only people 
who got to make them</font>

220
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">were artisans working under nobles.</font>

221
00:14:05,150 --> 00:14:08,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I thought I'd never get a chance 
to be involved! I'm so happy!</font>

222
00:14:08,920 --> 00:14:11,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He beat me to the punch.</i></font>

223
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:14,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Given Sigma-kun's ingenuity and drive,</i></font>

224
00:14:14,590 --> 00:14:18,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I hoped he'd attend the private school 
and eventually work at the palace.</i></font>

225
00:14:18,550 --> 00:14:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ideally, I wanted him for
the accounting department!</i></font>

226
00:14:22,410 --> 00:14:24,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kondu, we made something amazing!</font>

227
00:14:24,530 --> 00:14:27,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's based on Sigma's idea. 
It's only a prototype,</font>

228
00:14:27,760 --> 00:14:30,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but we can actually measure 
magical energy with this!</font>

229
00:14:30,480 --> 00:14:31,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please tell me the details.</font>

230
00:14:32,170 --> 00:14:37,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey. You were hospitalized in the 
infirmary until your discharge just now.</font>

231
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:41,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's with the sudden burst
 of motivation to work?!</font>

232
00:14:41,400 --> 00:14:43,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? B-But, I mean...</font>

233
00:14:44,010 --> 00:14:45,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We're going home.</font>

234
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:46,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay...</font>

235
00:14:47,110 --> 00:14:49,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ist-san, please write up a...</font>

236
00:14:50,420 --> 00:14:52,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yeah, not happening.</i></font>

237
00:14:52,700 --> 00:14:57,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">U-Um, I wrote a simple summary of 
the mechanism and materials we used.</font>

238
00:14:58,800 --> 00:15:01,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sigma-kun, you're the best!</font>

239
00:15:01,340 --> 00:15:03,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? It's nothing, really.</font>

240
00:15:03,370 --> 00:15:07,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I always saw these kinds of 
documents at my boss's place.</font>

241
00:15:08,530 --> 00:15:12,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's so brilliant. How wonderful.</i></font>

242
00:15:12,010 --> 00:15:14,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I want him for the accounting
department after all.</i></font>

243
00:15:14,490 --> 00:15:19,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, if he went into the sorcery 
department, my life would be a lot easier.</i></font>

244
00:15:19,960 --> 00:15:21,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What a dilemma!</i></font>

245
00:15:21,940 --> 00:15:25,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you remember what I just said?</font>

246
00:15:25,600 --> 00:15:27,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, of course.</font>

247
00:15:27,100 --> 00:15:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's go home.</font>

248
00:15:28,060 --> 00:15:30,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll take my time to go over it there...</font>

249
00:15:30,190 --> 00:15:31,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ow, ow, ow!</font>

250
00:15:31,750 --> 00:15:33,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me.</font>

251
00:15:33,820 --> 00:15:36,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What are you doing to Master 
Seiichiro after he just recovered?!</font>

252
00:15:38,430 --> 00:15:42,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is nothing, Siegvold-sama. 
Please don't worry about it.</font>

253
00:15:42,610 --> 00:15:46,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aresh-sama, I'm the one at fault. 
Please let me go...</font>

254
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's enough, Aresh!</font>

255
00:15:51,100 --> 00:15:55,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro, 
are you in better health?</font>

256
00:15:55,310 --> 00:15:57,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, thank you very much.</font>

257
00:16:03,560 --> 00:16:05,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Siegvold-sama?</font>

258
00:16:05,780 --> 00:16:08,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I came because I heard you 
were being discharged.</font>

259
00:16:09,370 --> 00:16:14,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please let me know if I can be of any help
regarding what we spoke of the other day.</font>

260
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be on my way.</font>

261
00:16:19,550 --> 00:16:21,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What we spoke of the other day...</i></font>

262
00:16:22,930 --> 00:16:25,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, about that...</font>

263
00:16:26,600 --> 00:16:32,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ball of magical energy that flew our
 way that day wasn't just an accident.</font>

264
00:16:32,240 --> 00:16:33,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

265
00:16:33,370 --> 00:16:38,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I learned of the situation
 from Prince Yurius</font>

266
00:16:38,070 --> 00:16:40,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">after Commander Indolark carried you away.</font>

267
00:16:41,320 --> 00:16:43,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A child present at the time remarked</font>

268
00:16:43,940 --> 00:16:47,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">that the prayer and incantation 
were notably different from usual.</font>

269
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I foolishly failed to notice it 
while I was talking with you.</font>

270
00:16:53,290 --> 00:16:58,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, Master Ist remembered 
every word of it and informed me.</font>

271
00:16:58,890 --> 00:17:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't the normal prayer we use,</font>

272
00:17:01,660 --> 00:17:04,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but one that consumes far 
more magic than necessary.</font>

273
00:17:04,590 --> 00:17:08,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I tried to stop it, but someone 
intentionally triggered an explosive surge</i></font>

274
00:17:08,970 --> 00:17:12,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>from the child who lost control 
and shot it at Kondu.</i></font>

275
00:17:13,840 --> 00:17:15,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The only one capable of such a thing...</font>

276
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:19,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now, let us begin the prayer.</font>

277
00:17:20,150 --> 00:17:21,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cipriano...</i></font>

278
00:17:21,870 --> 00:17:23,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Is he trying to cover up the embezzlement?</i></font>

279
00:17:24,390 --> 00:17:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Even so, his methods...</i></font>

280
00:17:27,050 --> 00:17:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">However, there isn't any definitive proof,</font>

281
00:17:29,500 --> 00:17:32,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so we've been quietly 
conducting an investigation.</font>

282
00:17:32,960 --> 00:17:34,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Master Seiichiro.</font>

283
00:17:34,710 --> 00:17:40,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I promise you that I will testify fully 
and truthfully, no matter the situation.</font>

284
00:17:44,760 --> 00:17:47,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Then, while I was hospitalized,</i></font>

285
00:17:47,850 --> 00:17:50,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cipriano submitted the 
income and expenses report,</i></font>

286
00:17:50,550 --> 00:17:53,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>bringing my temporary assignment 
to the church to an end.</i></font>

287
00:17:54,320 --> 00:17:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome home, Aresh-sama and Kondu-sama.</font>

288
00:17:58,800 --> 00:18:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's good to be back.</font>

289
00:18:00,670 --> 00:18:02,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We were so worried!</font>

290
00:18:02,890 --> 00:18:05,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll make sure to bring 
you back to full health!</font>

291
00:18:06,230 --> 00:18:07,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thank you very much.</font>

292
00:18:25,700 --> 00:18:29,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I knew it. There's no similarity at all.</i></font>

293
00:18:32,830 --> 00:18:35,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There's nothing left for me 
to do at the church.</i></font>

294
00:18:36,410 --> 00:18:39,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for the private school,
Her Holiness and His Highness</i></font>

295
00:18:39,890 --> 00:18:42,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>are heading the project with my support.</i></font>

296
00:18:43,150 --> 00:18:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>As for the finances,</i></font>

297
00:18:44,610 --> 00:18:47,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>all I had to do was submit the 
paperwork to Prime Mister Camile.</i></font>

298
00:18:49,230 --> 00:18:52,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So why was I the one targeted?</i></font>

299
00:18:52,860 --> 00:18:54,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Something doesn't sit right...</i></font>

300
00:18:56,160 --> 00:18:58,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Seiichirou, are you all right?</font>

301
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:01,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not to worry. I'm perfectly fine.</font>

302
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:03,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You've lost a little weight.</font>

303
00:19:03,730 --> 00:19:05,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I?</font>

304
00:19:05,240 --> 00:19:07,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like you're the one 
who's lost some weight.</font>

305
00:19:08,380 --> 00:19:11,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It tends to happen when 
an expedition runs long.</font>

306
00:19:11,300 --> 00:19:13,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're already thin to begin with,</font>

307
00:19:13,720 --> 00:19:16,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so you really need to take 
better care of your health.</font>

308
00:19:16,120 --> 00:19:16,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay.</font>

309
00:19:17,330 --> 00:19:21,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Really? You're quick to lie.</font>

310
00:19:21,700 --> 00:19:24,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I really did take my time
and rest properly.</font>

311
00:19:24,940 --> 00:19:29,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aren't you the one who isn't 
properly resting, Aresh-sama?</font>

312
00:19:30,150 --> 00:19:32,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine now.</font>

313
00:19:33,110 --> 00:19:34,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for worrying you.</font>

314
00:19:38,640 --> 00:19:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I was pretty worried when Aresh-sama 
immediately went to hunt magic beasts</i></font>

315
00:19:43,680 --> 00:19:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>right after the purification expedition, 
but does he realize that?</i></font>

316
00:19:48,160 --> 00:19:50,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, Aresh-sama...</font>

317
00:19:50,550 --> 00:19:51,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

318
00:19:51,970 --> 00:19:54,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything you wish for?</font>

319
00:19:55,110 --> 00:19:56,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

320
00:19:56,340 --> 00:19:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'd have to be something
 I can provide, though.</font>

321
00:19:59,640 --> 00:20:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there anything you'd like 
me to do or get for you?</font>

322
00:20:03,990 --> 00:20:07,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd like to thank you 
for saving my life again.</font>

323
00:20:08,090 --> 00:20:11,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But you won't take monetary 
compensation, right?</font>

324
00:20:13,070 --> 00:20:14,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course not.</font>

325
00:20:14,960 --> 00:20:20,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I want to do something 
to pay you back in a different way.</font>

326
00:20:22,450 --> 00:20:24,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It could be anything.</font>

327
00:20:24,430 --> 00:20:28,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my savior, so I'm willing 
to do just about anything for you.</font>

328
00:20:36,480 --> 00:20:38,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything, you say?</font>

329
00:20:38,740 --> 00:20:40,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anything.</font>

330
00:20:40,920 --> 00:20:43,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Not that I'll quit my job, though.</i></font>

331
00:20:44,610 --> 00:20:49,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">In that case, change the
 way you speak to me.</font>

332
00:20:50,580 --> 00:20:51,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

333
00:20:52,600 --> 00:20:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Have I said something rude to you?</font>

334
00:20:56,080 --> 00:20:57,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, that's not it.</font>

335
00:20:57,960 --> 00:21:01,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm telling you to change
 your tone with me.</font>

336
00:21:02,180 --> 00:21:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My tone?</font>

337
00:21:04,400 --> 00:21:08,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to speak to me 
like you do that boy.</font>

338
00:21:09,380 --> 00:21:10,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

339
00:21:10,910 --> 00:21:14,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, do you mean Sigma-kun?</font>

340
00:21:15,020 --> 00:21:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a stall vendor 
and I hire him for work,</font>

341
00:21:18,740 --> 00:21:21,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so the dynamic is completely different.</font>

342
00:21:22,160 --> 00:21:23,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So what?</font>

343
00:21:24,640 --> 00:21:29,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm closer to you than a child like that!</font>

344
00:21:31,540 --> 00:21:36,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In other words, this noble who has a face 
as beautiful as a sculpted masterpiece</i></font>

345
00:21:36,230 --> 00:21:39,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and is the strongest knight 
in the kingdom is jealous</i></font>

346
00:21:39,410 --> 00:21:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>of a little boy barely 
over ten years of age?</i></font>

347
00:21:46,740 --> 00:21:48,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My chest hurts...</font>

348
00:21:49,090 --> 00:21:52,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Where? How does it hurt?! Let me see!</font>

349
00:21:52,390 --> 00:21:53,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's not it...</font>

350
00:21:53,690 --> 00:21:57,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just that it's been a while since 
my heartstrings were tugged like this.</font>

351
00:21:57,270 --> 00:21:59,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not an illness or anything...</font>

352
00:22:00,660 --> 00:22:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is too much.</i></font>

353
00:23:35,010 --> 00:23:40,090
<font face="Trebuchet MS" size="24">{\an8}EPISODE 12
WE CORNERED HIM. AND THEN...</font>

